name: Amanda Nutton
text: He is amazing.  The best Magic show I have ever experienced.  We had him for our sons birthday party and the kids were amazed with his skills.  I also seen him at a work function and I was blown away, could not figure out his tricks at all.  Recommend him for any event, very entertaining.

name: Lupe Albizo
text:
(Translated by Google) Love it
